19:T420,HME (Heat and Moisture Exchanger) filters are well-established respiratory consumables used in mechanical ventilation to provide passive humidification and filtration. Internal evidence clearly describes function and application. However, 'OXSOL' brand requires verification - no external evidence confirms Meril manufactures an 'OXSOL' branded HME filter line. Meril's website confirms they operate in endo-surgery and multiple device categories, but no specific mention of respiratory/HME products found. The reference to 'endo-surgical equipment' in brochure_description is unusual for HME filters (typically ICU/respiratory equipment). This may be: (1) OXSOL is a valid Meril respiratory brand not visible in public sources, (2) product misclassified or mislabeled, or (3) product from acquisition/partnership. Clinical classification as HME filter consumable is confident based on description, but brand/manufacturer relationship needs internal verification. Recommend review to confirm OXSOL brand ownership and Meril's respiratory product portfolio.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"OXSOL HME Filters","product_name_display":"OXSOL HME Filters","sku_code":"MRL-OXS-016","product_family":"OXSOL HME Filters","product_family_display":"OXSOL HME Filters","slug":"oxsol-hme-filters","images":[{"id":"015d1b3a61fd","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3dee16be148669108824a/cc_cover_51ff670c.jpg","original_filename":"critical_care_p6.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":328495,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:06:38.211321+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction"}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"OXSOL HME Filters | OXSOL Respiratory Care - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"OXSOL HME Filters deliver superior heat and moisture exchange for optimal breathing circuit humidification in respiratory care applications. These advanced f...","pack_size":"Single filter","size_variables":[],"created_at":"2026-03-25T13: